Changes I made:<br>
1) Edited that inventory. It was way to messed up. As you can see it turned out looking like Kalv's =)<br>
<br>
2) I changed the spell Gem locations so they were horizontal and not diagnal. and put the spell book icon to the right of the last spell gem.<br>
<br>
3) I edited that track so It was more Druid/Bard friendly<br>
<br>
4) took out the Percent for the Sta since it doesn't work anyhow (but i kept the sta bar because I have a Druid and Warrior ALT)<br>
<br>
5) I changed what was on the Window select some. (it is little segment to the right of the bottom chat window) I made It so I had access to My Woven Grass BP and my Woven Grass Bracer. I kept the Secondary there not for My druid but for my Bard for easy instrument changes with the instruments in the inventory which as in everyone else's is to the right.<br>
<br>
6) nothing specially but i threw My guild's Initials just above the spell book button on the spell gem window.<br>
<br>
If i get requests i will upload a Zip file with the stuff. In the zip i won't have my guild's Initials there because I doubt you really want them there haha.<br>
<br>
And there are a few changes i am looking to do aswell. Some of which include lengthening some of the windows that don't quite line up right. (window select and group windows specificly.) and Relocating the spell cast bar from it's current location (under the wieght.) <p><center><a href=http://home.earthlink.net/~psighco/oswp/index.html>Order Of the Scattered Winds Portraits</a></center>
