I guess looking at this I could just move my buff window to the left side of the screen and get the mirror image of what I want, but where's the fun in that? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> add Primary/Secondary slots to bags when they are opened</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Generally, if I am opening a bag it is to swap out something (for instance I go from epic/thyxl to opal stein/opal stein for selling VT to NPC's). It would be nice to do the entire swap from within the bag and not have to move the mouse away from the bag at all. <p><b><a href="mailto:salamane@hotmail.com">Salamane Inglorion</a></b><br>
