One other thing I do to free up space. Get rid of the Pet box (Alt-F1) and the Actions box in lower right (Alt-M). Then drop your buff box the way I suggested to just tiny icons and the rest pushed off the screen. Then move your other stuff over. That gives you room for a 3rd chat box or whatever you want.<br>
